   • openfoam2306 → source /usr/lib/openfoam/openfoam2306/etc/bashrc
   • openfoam2312 → source /usr/lib/openfoam/openfoam2312/etc/bashrc
   • openfoam2412 → source /usr/lib/openfoam/openfoam2412/etc/bashrc
   • foam-extend-4.0 → source /opt/foam/foam-extend-4.0/etc/bashrc
